Introduction
Welcome to PlayPixo (“we,” “our,” or “us”). We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing a secure experience while using our app, PlayPixo (“the App”). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information. By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.
Information We Collect
We collect information in the following ways:
